ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectRegulations Amending and Repealing Certain Regulations Made Under the Financial Administration Act
PrecisRegulations Amending and Repealing CERTAIN REGULATIONS MADE UNDER THE FINANCIAL ADMINISTRATION ACT in order to bring amendments to the Fees in Respect of Drugs and Medical Devices Regulations and the repeal of the Authority to Sell Veterinary Drugs Fees Regulations, the Veterinary Drug Evaluation Fees Regulations and the Establishment Licensing Fees (Veterinary Drugs) Regulations, all of which fall under the Financial Administration Act, will provide clarity to stakeholders on which set of fees are in force and prevent duplicative fees.
